KI/Localization+and+Translation+-+How+to" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Here’s a quick guide on how to get started</span></a><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class=""> </span></div></li></ul><h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:8pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;" class="">Developers</span></h3><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" class=""><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.17" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Download</span></a><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class=""> and </span><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Installing+Ushahidi+3.x" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Install the platform</span></a></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Setting+up+an+Ushahidi+3.x+development+build" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Set up a development build</span></a></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><div styl